longBusinessSummary: Wind Works Power Corp. operates a 4.6 megawatt (MW) producing wind farm in Germany. It is also developing 50 MW of Feed-in Tariff contracted projects and 10 MW Cloudy Ridge project in Ontario; 77 MW of near-term permitted projects in Germany; and a project pipeline in the United States. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Ottawa, Canada.
